OL,4,                               U'a|wk
OL,5,B"What in the name of Charlie  U`///{5n'
OL,6,BDick am I doing on this page? U*~}|>
OL,7,BI hate this page! While I'm   U8<;6
OL,8,Bhere I might as well take the Um}e/!'
OL,9,Bopportunity to do some reviewing.      
OL,11,F"Over the past year these Digitiser    
OL,12,Fsaps have gone all stupid, by marking  
OL,13,Fcertain games far too high.            
OL,15,B"I am here to readdress the balance by 
OL,16,Btaking the Digitiser reviews by the    
OL,17,Bneck and punching them in the Jimmy    
OL,18,BBolans. You know what I mean."         
