OL,3,EMARIO KART 64GNintendo 64 `````````````
OL,5,B"There isn't a human being on earth who
OL,6,Bdidn't love the original Mario Kart.   
OL,7,BThe principles of its gameplay were    
OL,8,Bunquestionably great.                  
OL,10,F"How then did Nintendo manage to make  
OL,11,Fsuch a dog's ear of the sequel? I mean,
OL,12,Fthey only had FIVE YEARS to get it     
OL,13,Fright. Idiots.                         
OL,15,B"Mario Kart was never about huge,      
OL,16,Bsprawling tracks - it was about tight  
OL,17,Bcourses with loads of potential for    
OL,18,Bsmacking your opponents up a bit."     
