OL,3,EMARIO KART 64GNintendo 64 `````````````
OL,5,B"Mario Kart 64 was one of the most     
OL,6,Beagerly-awaited games of all time. Fans
OL,7,Bof the original had patiently awaited a
OL,8,Bsequel for half a decade, and when it  
OL,9,Barrived it wasn't a patch on the first 
OL,10,BMario Kart.                            
OL,12,F"If ever there were evidence that      
OL,13,Fproducer Shigeru Miyamoto were over    
OL,14,Fstretched, then this is it. I cannot   
OL,15,Fstress how stinked-up this game is."   
